&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;The western divide on the way to Cluj, here is the spring of the Crisul Repede (&quot;fast&quot;) river that flows westward. From here on, going east, it's Cluj teritory.&lt;/p&gt;<br />
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;ctl00_ContentBody_LongDescription&quot;&gt;Please hide carefully. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
<p><em>This <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/viewcache.php?cacheid=166'>geocache</a> description comes from the <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/'>Opencaching.RO</a> site.</em></p>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;ctl00_ContentBody_LongDescription&quot;&gt;Beyond Ploiesti where hills begin to rise you'll find a valley covered by forests, criss-crossed by torrents coming from the north.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br />
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;ctl00_ContentBody_LongDescription&quot;&gt;Many paths lay before you, combine and choose your trail at will, easier, for the light hearted, steeper, up and down and round the hills for the experienced, you cand spend many days exploring them hills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
<p><em>This <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/viewcache.php?cacheid=195'>geocache</a> description comes from the <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/'>Opencaching.RO</a> site.</em></p>
